skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my mood
des:
Mood skill is used for when you're sad or happy and you want to share it with someone who understands how you feel. you can activate this skill by saying "Alexa open my mood"
Some of the things mood understands are:
-I am feeling sad
-I am heartbroken
-Happy
Mood is here to tell you exactly what you want to listen to.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
